    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IDOLZ is a multiplayer fighting game where punching isn’t enough — you also need to know how to insult.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During each match, customized insults fill your flow bar, letting you unleash your character’s special move at the right moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced battles, unique characters, and a system that keeps every match fresh and unpredictable.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/60de8e5ebdb81be791e09cd6902cbd3e.poster.avif?t=1758796207\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/60de8e5ebdb81be791e09cd6902cbd3e.webm?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/60de8e5ebdb81be791e09cd6902cbd3e.mp4?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPECIALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Specials don’t just deal damage — they humiliate.</strong><br>Each one features a unique animation designed to land right when it matters most.<br><strong>From diamond showers to out-of-control androids, specials in IDOLZ can shift the fight in seconds.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/585246ca947446dc58b91e25dfb5576e.poster.avif?t=1758796207\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/585246ca947446dc58b91e25dfb5576e.webm?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/585246ca947446dc58b91e25dfb5576e.mp4?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROASTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Insults are part of the fight.</strong><br>During the match, throw roasts to pressure your opponent and charge your flow bar to gain the upper hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With voices from Foyone, Spok Sponha, and Celedonio, among others. <br><strong>Choose between soft, medium or extreme levels in every round.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/aeb6e8b6bb0c6fbf354bb12301c7e524.poster.avif?t=1758796207\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/aeb6e8b6bb0c6fbf354bb12301c7e524.webm?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/aeb6e8b6bb0c6fbf354bb12301c7e524.mp4?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZATION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create your style by choosing your character, skin, music, intro animation, celebration and insults.</strong><br>Everything is customizable so each match feels like yours.<br><strong>Set the tone from the first hit to the final word.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/6040a3efa5490a498fc1d84343e17344.poster.avif?t=1758796207\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/6040a3efa5490a498fc1d84343e17344.webm?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138400/extras/6040a3efa5490a498fc1d84343e17344.mp4?t=1758796207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONLINE COMPETITIVE MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1v1 online battles. Straightforward and unfiltered.</strong><br><strong>Fast fights, sharp insults, and guaranteed laughs.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
